    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's really capturing that specific historical viewpoint. To round out the character, can you add a section where he explains why he believes their intellect or social capacity is inherently different from his own men? I want him to justify why the empire has the right to lead them, perhaps touching on how their natural state is more instinctual compared to the European mind.",
